}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== ''LubanCat 1'' and LubanCat logo are on top of board.
{{See also|List of Single-board computers}}
===Hardware specification=== *CPU: [[Rockchip]] RK3566 @1.8GHz :Quad-Core ARM (Cortex-A55) *GPU: ''Mali-G52 2EE'' (OpenGL ES3.2); NPU 0.8Tops @INT8 :VPU (with 4K VP9 and 4K 10-bit H265/H264 decoding) *Storage: 32GB eMMC 5.1, TF card (max.512GB)/MMC card slot *Memory: 4GB (LPDDR4) SDRAM *USB: 1x USB 3.0 Host, 3x USB 2.0 Host, :1x USB 2.0 (Type-C) (OTG/Power) ports *PCI: 1x miniPCIe slot *GPIO: 1x 40-pin headers *Power Source: 5V/3A, USB (Type-C)
